wiki.content:
A song of hope, needing somebody to fulfill their dream of finding  a true love of their own.  The message they send  is that the person  they truly need to find does not have to be anybody special, or the fact their background  may have flaws or  of any particular type of abode. The most important requirement  would be total love  to be given, that's all they would need from that person...........
